1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:06,000
In the area around Pęgów,
people call it
a strawberry village.

2
00:00:06,000 --> 00:00:12,000
This comes from fields
full of strawberries
and a special event.

3
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:18,000
It is the Strawberry Festival
organized by a local association.

4
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:24,000
The festival has
over 20 years
of tradition.

5
00:00:24,000 --> 00:00:30,000
It did not take place
during the COVID time.

6
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:36,000
In 2026, it will be
the 18th edition.

7
00:00:36,000 --> 00:00:42,000
It is definitely worth
planning a visit!

8
00:00:42,000 --> 00:00:48,000
There are stage stars
and many attractions
for children.

9
00:00:48,000 --> 00:00:54,000
There are puppet shows
and an inflatable playground.

10
00:00:54,000 --> 00:01:00,000
There are also
exciting contests.

11
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:06,000
For example:
best strawberry cake
or best costume.

12
00:01:06,000 --> 00:01:12,000
You can even compete
in eating strawberries
for time.

13
00:01:12,000 --> 00:01:23,000
In Pęgów, strawberries are not just fruit—
they are a reason to celebrate!